snippet.title: YourYesi
snippet.description:
Hello there! Thank you for stopping by & checking out my channel. My name is Yesi & I am a certified Makeup Artist & licensed cosmetologist. I've been taught by celebrity makeup artists & currently working in mostly bridal makeup but I've done fashion runway & photoshoots as well. I have had some of my work featured in magazines & my passion is helping people to look & feel beatiful inside & out. I post videos every Wednesday, so please subscribe so you can stay posted on new videos. I am always open to honest feedback, so don't be shy. Hope you guys enjoy & thanks again for watching.

Xoxo!
Snapchat: @makeupyesi

For business inquiries only email: yesimeister@gmail.com
